{{Otheruses|Fever}}
'''Hesken Fever''' was a non-[[Death/Legends|fatal]] disease caused by bacteria that thrived in [[Vacuum/Legends|vacuum]].

[[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Alliance to Restore the Republic]] [[Pilot/Legends|pilot]] [[Wes Janson/Legends|Wes Janson]] contracted the disease suddenly while on a [[Scout/Legends|scouting]] mission, preventing his participation in the [[Battle of Yavin/Legends|assault]] on the [[DS-1 Orbital Battle Station/Legends|first Death Star]]. [[Jek Tono Porkins/Legends|Jek Tono Porkins]] took his place instead, and was [[Death/Legends|killed]] during the battle.

